metadata.name: Vinyl Dance
metadata.description:
Dance, like nobody is watching!

Imagine, a preparation before the wedding when bride made a little Vinyl Dance with her favourite music!

...

This was a very beautiful session with snow-white vinyl record: Billy Idol - White Wedding. 

Skin tone is beautifully harmonizing with sunlight and golden elements in interior... while petticoat and the record - with white light and the piano.

...

P.S. This is a FullHD version. I'll give you a 4K version if you want!
